A massive green Android robot mascot standing triumphantly atop a crumbling mountain of obsolete flip phones and old smartphones, depicted in vivid comic book style with bold ink outlines and dynamic halftone dot shading. The robot strikes a confident pose with one foot planted on a crushed device, arms raised victoriously against a dramatic orange and yellow starburst background. Scattered around the base are defeated phone brands rendered as broken mechanical parts and circuit boards. The perspective is dramatic low-angle, emphasizing the Android's dominance. Deep shadows and high contrast colors typical of classic American comics, with action lines radiating outward suggesting explosive change and disruption in the mobile landscape.
